data.title: Lottie Williams
data.meta_description: Lottie Williams. Actress: Opfer einer großen Liebe. Lottie Williams was born on 20 January 1874 in Indianapolis, Indiana, USA. She was an actress, known for Opfer einer großen Liebe (1939), Yesterday's Wife (1923) and Der steinige Weg (1923). She died on 16 November 1962 in Los Angeles, California, USA.
data.text: Lottie Williams was born on January 20, 1874 in Indianapolis, Indiana, USA. She was an actress, known for Opfer einer großen Liebe (1939), Yesterday's Wife (1923) and Der steinige Weg (1923). She died on November 16, 1962 in Los Angeles, California, USA.
